<plot>In 'Three Little Words', Casey (Hanzo Hamamura) has just a few short minutes to decide whether or not to reveal his true feelings for Alex (Laine Yoshioka) before she leaves his life. Through Casey's eyes, we see the memories that the two shared together, from how they met to how they ended up at that very moment, the moment where Casey has to decide if he'll say those three little words that make all the difference.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?605761</url></doc>
